## Coverage Completion Checklist
- [ ] Every touched Path ID appears in the table
- [ ] Every touched row has Smoke Coverage status
- [ ] No touched row says `Coverage pending`
- [ ] Smoke command/runbook evidence recorded
- [ ] Manual rows point to concrete runbooks or exact steps
- [ ] State Mutation Index paths exist in the repo
- [ ] Retired pathways noted in `CHANGELOG.md`
